window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Old demons are back.</p> <p>Maddie’s dealing with the fallout of her choices. Safety and happiness are relative, elusive things she’s desperate to have. But they will forever remain out of reach until the demons of her past are laid to rest.</p> <p>Tyler’s mistakes resurface to haunt him, and he’s just beginning to understand that money can’t fix a broken relationship. He must open his heart and search for answers he’d rather not find.</p> <p>She wants peace in a world made of chaos.</p> <p>He wants to rid himself of a lifetime of guilt.</p> <p>They’re soul mates, but that’s no guarantee. They’ll need to rely on each other to find their happily ever after.&nbsp;</p> <p>Because the fight never ends - it just gets easier with someone at your side.</p>"; 
